26T05:48:15.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到幾左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"644fbe08e563e9817572822f69cf8a6c0c333ba2","tid":2380491,"uid":44298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9021f4197065630cbce766a552c5a0dfffa4aa22","tid":2380491,"uid":117893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee0fda119580f4525c2078e603cabd1037948467","tid":2380491,"uid":70964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bec5aa6943f87ae595f0623a9fed00744142f0b6","tid":2380491,"uid":387461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9503c8d68d57a08cbf6eb5e75278695c9f0f835","tid":2380491,"uid":45353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d21e58ec6503775ca1413a480936aa2cecd2c9e5","tid":2380491,"uid":70964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"40f5ac51aac5169569cbad73dd2c87ed850db382","tid":2380491,"uid":88002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:51:42.000Z","msg":"瞓緊覺, 朝早起身就發覺封左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:55:42.000Z","msg":"應該星期五/六/日最大機會<br />\n封區開始時間  ( 2300 - 0300 )"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:51:03.000Z","msg":"咁就唔係突擊"},{"pid":"09528d3